how to beat the high cost of living is a 1980 american comedy film starring jane curtin , susan saint james and jessica lange . also in the cast are dabney coleman , fred willard , richard benjamin , eddie albert , cathryn damon , and a cameo by jane curtin 's fellow saturday night live co-star garrett morris . the movie was released in summer of 1980 , grossing approximately us $ 7.5 million . this was the final american international pictures production before its merger with filmways .